.000Z","msg":"他們說，今天又有人被斬了。我憤怒。<br />\n然後他們告訴，還有人被咬下一根耳朵呢，就在地上，我問，為甚麼電視上都沒有？"},{"pid":"fea282af49050eddabaaed48278b74da56589a3b","tid":1691124,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"主流媒體會不播嗎？他們說，你懂的。<br />\n不是呀，我看見有人被打呀，在電視上，但沒有耳朵。<br />\n是的，你能看甚麼，聽甚麼，都是被控製的。"},{"pid":"936b6ea1445fd139f015c52230a5414c346fd4b4","tid":1691124,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce129afa3d4ee21c9cfe0fb3fb9bf936ed98a24","tid":1691124,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"880865b435faacd890a7c39a0a64e31d07b3c0d7","tid":1691124,"uid":196991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"721"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"nothing happyed"},{"pid":"a03a4e336944ab6aa2d5c47b3b1093bdf1c74407","tid":1691124,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"無力感很重，但仍然要有希望，因為希望的力量大於絕望"},{"pid":"f6ec7512f7bf2aa30d72d2b7b4f6ba88de5bf810","tid":1691124,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"如果有一天，你累了，請好好休息，休息，其實是為了繼續，向前行"},{"pid":"88a93591809f6ded7e2dd5e3a7b9824c6ea8ead8","tid":1691124,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"夢想何價？"},{"pid":"62e8cc07c6f70bc52c2d2ae4804ecc4fc4fc51ac","tid":1691124,"uid":141601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"堅持何價？"},{"pid":"ba87eb0c1a0e8bafc769f3e032e8327db8fa0388","tid":1691124,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:04:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"831d9d7970da14bbbe9188525d10b0aa531a5a2a","tid":1691124,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:06:09.000Z","msg":