/>\nTVB係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>品牌負資產</strong></span></span>，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">品牌形象將付諸流水</span></span></strong>！無人可憐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB今個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到年底啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga<br />\n<br />\n是晚重溫@3 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美素佳兒</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frisohk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrisohk%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=cb657640\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frisohk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZERePB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZERePB.jpg&h=b442cec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【美素佳兒做咩？】<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>蟲蟲奶粉邊個食 冇人食冇人食</strong></span></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">美素佳兒奶粉驚現蟲屍，食環署介入調查。市民張先生上月中在銅鑼灣購買多罐美素佳兒三號奶粉，數日後開罐沖奶餵廿個月大的女兒，惟愛女飲了兩次後，張再打開奶粉罐時，赫然發現罐內有一條約四毫米的物體，疑似蟲屍。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20121102/00176_017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20121102%2F00176_017.html&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=fae98678\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20121102/00176_017.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>量匙容量不相符 隨時餓親BB</strong></span></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">美素佳兒宣布因附送的量匙與原本藍色量匙不相符，為避免混淆消費者，將自願回收「皇家美素力」嬰兒配方奶粉。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/858331/即時-香港-美素佳兒-皇家美素力-奶粉量匙不符-消費者可更換退款\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F858331%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E7%B4%A0%E4%BD%B3%E5%85%92-%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%B6%E7%BE%8E%E7%B4%A0%E5%8A%9B-%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E9%87%8F%E5%8C%99%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6-%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B%E9%80%80%E6%AC%BE&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=b7bec172\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F858331%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E7%B4%A0%E4%BD%B3%E5%85%92-%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%B6%E7%BE%8E%E7%B4%A0%E5%8A%9B-%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89%E9%87%8F%E5%8C%99%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6-%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B%E9%80%80%E6%AC%BE&h=c5e4b479\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/858331/即時-香港-美素佳兒-皇家美素力-奶粉量匙不符-消費者可更換退款</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>美素媽咪會貴價兼洩私隱</strong></span></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">經媽咪會出售的奶粉，價錢亦會較正常藥房奶粉的建議零售價為高。按消委會去年12月調查數據，美素佳兒的建議零售價最多較藥房價貴18%；美贊臣建議零售價也較藥房價最多貴3.9%。港媽透過媽咪會訂購要捱貴奶粉之餘，亦要於入會時提交個人資料，變相讓奶粉商借機收集顧客資料，作產品推廣之用。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130126/18146964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130126%2F18146964&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=77ed8445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130126%2F18146964&h=421b00b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130126/18146964</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>限制供應逼媽媽捱貴奶粉</strong></span></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">美素佳兒繼被指向藥房綑綁式賣奶粉後，再被指集中供貨予連鎖個人護理用品店。有藥房負責人質疑，美素佳兒早前指增加供應至100萬罐，當中可能有約七成供應予連鎖店，其餘供應予藥房，令市民不能從藥房以低於正價（建議零售價）買奶粉。</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130206/18157976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130206%2F18157976&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=779417ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130206%2F18157976&h=4fbc4476\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130206/18157976</a><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>再唔撤budget，業績定仆直！<br />\n盡快同TVB割席！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n※請善用template，清晰表達訴求<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XwyKzUR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwyKzUR.jpg&h=044cdbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/XwyKzUR.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXwyKzUR.jpg&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=1d9f1ac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/XwyKzUR.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=b4e39086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=8d59233f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=8342130d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝大家</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"天日搞tempo好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://buzznews.news/view2/9337/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuzznews.news%2Fview2%2F9337%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=8ccb4e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://buzznews.news/view2/9337/</a>"},{"pid":"1fe1518f93ea08e0496593ddf094606a0734d683","tid":1691124,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:50:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日以繼夜，不斷唱衰示威者</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGJCa37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGJCa37.jpg&h=7c66f1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tgFwZXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtgFwZXz.jpg&h=87967957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzrTtQZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail